channel.title: Ps-Revolution Project
channel.description:
Help! Need Alpha Testers! Hello guys,
I am making a 317, from the source Tragedy PK,
I have changed the client a bit and some cleaned the source a bit, I ALSO NEED :
1 Forum Admin [0/1] <-- must know vbulletin, I am very strong with vbulletin so prepare for a test.
1 InGame Mod [0/1] <-- Prepare also for a test
What I need from you : Come on and help me find bugs/glitches Tell me what should be added or is needed
REMINDER :
This will be an Economy/Player Killing Server. So dont tel me to add stupid things.
What we will have :
A great Server, Vbulletin Forums <-- Under Construction ATM.
Please come help!
Thanks, EDIT : Build.bat BEFORE running the client! Thanks. Download : 30MB *
I will be on right after my smoke
madmike1225@hotmail.com is my email and skype : madmike1225
Dont Hate/Flame I dont care im just alpha testing at the moment :/
